{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/komikus-samurai-x-ditahan-atas-tuduhan-pornografi-anak/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Komikus Samurai X Ditahan Atas Tuduhan Pornografi Anak","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Siapa sih yang gak kenal sama anime Samurai X, cerita Si Batosai Sang Pembantai. Komik manga dan anime karya Nobuhiro Watsuki ini merupakan salah satu anime terlaris sepanjang masa. Tapi ada kabar buruk datang dari sang <em>author</em> nih, bro sis. Karena pada hari Rabu lalu pihak Departemen Kepolisian Metropolitan Tokyo menahan sang komikus Nobuhiro Watsuki atas kepemilikan DVD pornografi anak-anak.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28499\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28499\" data-attachment-id=\"28499\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/komikus-samurai-x-ditahan-atas-tuduhan-pornografi-anak/attachment/isi-3-2-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-2-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : www.facebook.com/Nobuhiro-Watsuki)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : www.facebook.com/Nobuhiro-Watsuki)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-2-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-2-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28499\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : www.facebook.com/Nobuhiro-Watsuki)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-28499\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : www.facebook.com/Nobuhiro-Watsuki)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Polisi telah menemukan beberapa kepingan DVD pornografi anak-anak saat menggeledah kantornya. DVD tersebut berisi konten pornografi anak-anak perempuan di bawah umur tanpa menggunakan busana. Menurut penyidik kepolisian, video eksplisit tersebut menampilkan hal-hal yang tidak senonoh, hingga melibatkan anak perempuan berusia 10 tahun di dalamnya. Pihak kepolisian juga menduga bahwa Nobuhiro Watsuki sudah memiliki DVD tersebut sejak awal bulan Oktober 2017 lalu. Komikus anime Samurai X ini diduga pernah mengakui bahwa dirinya menyukai anak-anak SD sampai anak-anak kelas 2 SMP.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28493\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28493\" data-attachment-id=\"28493\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/komikus-samurai-x-ditahan-atas-tuduhan-pornografi-anak/attachment/isi-1-1-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : www.facebook.com/RurouniKenshinOfficial)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : www.facebook.com/RurouniKenshinOfficial)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-1-1.jpg\" data-l